flowchart TD
  A[Load index.html] --> B[Run main.js]
  B --> C[startApp]
  C --> D[Create elevators list]
  C --> E[Create UI and services]
  D --> F[Create ElevatorSystem]
  E --> F
  F --> G[Initialize UI and bind buttons]

  H[User clicks Call on a floor] --> I[ElevatorSystem.handleCall]
  I --> J[Add request to queue]
  J --> K[Button state = Waiting]
  K --> L[Dispatch work]

  L --> M{Any idle elevators?}
  M -- No --> N[Do nothing - keep request queued]
  M -- Yes --> O[Pick nearest idle elevator]
  O --> P[Mark elevator moving and animate]
  P --> Q[Beep + mark elevator arrived]
  Q --> R[Button state = Arrived + show time]
  R --> S[Wait 2 seconds]
  S --> T[Reset elevator and reset button]
  T --> L
